data.description: GREAT NEW PRICE! Welcome home to Huntington Ridge in Newburgh. This 2 story brick home offers 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths plus a bonus room. This traditional home has so much space, starting with the FORMAL DINING room at the entrance and also a OFFICE or den with French Doors. The large eat in KITCHEN has an island, plenty of cabinets and granite counters, plus  a walk in pantry. It is open to the FAMILY ROOM with brand new carpet, built ins and a fireplace. Rounding out the main level, is a LARGE laundry room with cabinets and counters for folding, PLUS a half bath. On the 2nd floor there are 4 bedrooms, 3 FULL baths, and a bonus room. The MASTER SUITE has an extra large bedroom, full bath, walk in closet, and an extra room for a variety of uses. This home has so much natural light throughout both levels. Outside there is landscaping, privacy fenced level backyard, back patio and a THREE CAR GARAGE. Don't miss your chance at this great home!
